text: FileZilla is a free Open Source FTP program. The program is designed for Windows, Linux and Mac OS X. FileZilla was the project of the month on SourceForge for November, 2003. ==History== Initially, FileZilla was created as a computer science class project in the second week of January 2001 by Tim Kosse and his two other classmates. ==Other websites== * FileZilla Website == References == Category:Software
